<plot>Over a ten year period Zoje Stage received nearly 1,000 rejections for her writing efforts. These letters - sometimes hopeful, sometimes impersonal, always ultimately negative - are the stars of this film. What keeps a writer going in the face of constant rejection? Creative compulsion. Eternal hope. Stupefying masochism.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?066463</url></doc>
